<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Fastball Futures — Precision Trading</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=DM+Mono:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300&family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --black: #050608;
    --deep: #0a0c10;
    --panel: #0f1116;
    --border: #1c2030;
    --accent: #00e5a0;
    --accent2: #ff4d2e;
    --dim: #3a4060;
    --muted: #6b7494;
    --text: #c8d0e8;
    --white: #eef2ff;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body { background: var(--black); color: var(--text); font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; overflow-x: hidden; cursor: crosshair; }

  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed; inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none; z-index: 999; opacity: 0.4;
  }

  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    padding: 20px 48px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: rgba(5,6,8,0.85); backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  }
  .logo { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--white); text-decoration: none; }
  .logo span { color: var(--accent); }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 36px; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  .nav-cta { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--accent); color: var(--accent); padding: 10px 22px; cursor: crosshair; transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s; }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--accent); color: var(--black); }

  #hero { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; padding: 120px 48px 80px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .hero-grid-lines {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,229,160,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,229,160,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
    mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 50%, black 30%, transparent 100%);
  }
  .hero-orb { position: absolute; width: 700px; height: 700px; border-radius: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,229,160,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%); top: -200px; right: -200px; pointer-events: none; }
  .hero-ticker { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--accent); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 28px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.2s forwards; }
  .hero-ticker::before { content: ''; width: 32px; height: 1px; background: var(--accent); }
  .hero-headline { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(5rem, 12vw, 11rem); line-height: 0.92; letter-spacing: 0.02em; color: var(--white); max-width: 900px; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.4s forwards; }
  .hero-headline .accent { color: var(--accent); }
  .hero-headline .stroke { -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(200,208,232,0.3); color: transparent; }
  .hero-sub { margin-top: 32px; max-width: 480px; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.04em; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.6s forwards; }
  .hero-actions { margin-top: 48px; display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: center; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.8s forwards; }
  .btn-primary { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; background: var(--accent); color: var(--black); border: none; padding: 16px 36px; cursor: crosshair; transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; font-weight: 500; }
  .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,229,160,0.3); }
  .btn-ghost { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; background: transparent; color: var(--muted); border: none; padding: 16px 0; cursor: crosshair; transition: color 0.2s; text-decoration: none; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--white); }
  .btn-ghost::after { content: '→'; }

  .stats-bar { position: absolute; bottom: 48px; left: 48px; right: 48px; display: flex; border: 1px solid var(--border); opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 1s forwards; }
  .stat-item { flex: 1; padding: 20px 32px; border-right: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .stat-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .stat-value { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 2.2rem; letter-spacing: 0.04em; color: var(--white); }
  .stat-value span { color: var(--accent); }
  .stat-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--dim); margin-top: 4px; }

  #approach { padding: 120px 48px; }
  .section-tag { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .section-tag::before { content: '//'; opacity: 0.5; }
  .section-headline { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5vw, 5rem); letter-spacing: 0.03em; color: var(--white); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 64px; }
  .section-headline em { font-style: normal; color: var(--accent); }

  .approach-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .approach-card { background: var(--deep); padding: 48px 40px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: background 0.3s; }
  .approach-card:hover { background: var(--panel); }
  .approach-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px; background: var(--accent); transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left; transition: transform 0.4s; }
  .approach-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
  .card-num { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 5rem; color: var(--border); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 24px; transition: color 0.3s; }
  .approach-card:hover .card-num { color: var(--dim); }
  .card-title { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.04em; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .card-body { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.03em; }

  #philosophy { padding: 120px 48px; background: var(--deep); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .philosophy-inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: center; }
  .big-quote { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 4.5rem); line-height: 1.05; color: var(--white); letter-spacing: 0.02em; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .big-quote .highlight { color: var(--accent); }
  .philosophy-body { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.85; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.03em; max-width: 420px; }

  .scorecard { background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 40px; position: relative; }
  .scorecard::before { content: 'TRADE LOG'; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--dim); position: absolute; top: 20px; left: 40px; }
  .trade-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 16px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); margin-top: 20px; }
  .trade-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .trade-ticker { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.3rem; letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: var(--white); }
  .trade-type { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 2px; }
  .trade-result { text-align: right; }
  .trade-pnl { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500; }
  .trade-pnl.win { color: var(--accent); }
  .trade-pnl.loss { color: var(--accent2); }
  .trade-size { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.62rem; color: var(--dim); margin-top: 2px; }
  .scorecard-footer { margin-top: 24px; padding-top: 20px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .win-rate { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 3.5rem; color: var(--accent); line-height: 1; }
  .win-rate-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.16em; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 4px; }
  .win-bar { width: 180px; }
  .win-bar-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.14em; color: var(--dim); margin-bottom: 8px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .win-bar-track { height: 4px; background: var(--border); }
  .win-bar-fill { height: 100%; width: 73%; background: var(--accent); position: relative; }
  .win-bar-fill::after { content: ''; position: absolute; right: 0; top: -3px; width: 2px; height: 10px; background: var(--accent); }

  #rules { padding: 120px 48px; }
  .rules-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr; gap: 80px; align-items: start; }
  .rules-sticky { position: sticky; top: 100px; }
  .rules-list { list-style: none; counter-reset: rule-counter; }
  .rules-list li { counter-increment: rule-counter; display: flex; gap: 24px; padding: 32px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .rules-list li:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .rule-counter { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--dim); padding-top: 6px; min-width: 28px; }
  .rule-counter::before { content: counter(rule-counter, decimal-leading-zero); }
  .rule-title { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: 0.04em; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .rule-desc { font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.03em; }

  #about { padding: 120px 48px; background: var(--deep); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: start; }
  .about-body { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.9; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.03em; }
  .about-body p + p { margin-top: 20px; }
  .about-body strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 400; }

  #contact { padding: 120px 48px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .contact-inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; }
  .form-field { margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .form-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--dim); display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .form-input, .form-textarea { width: 100%; background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text); font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; padding: 14px 18px; outline: none; transition: border-color 0.2s; cursor: crosshair; resize: none; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  .form-input:focus, .form-textarea:focus { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .form-textarea { height: 130px; }
  .form-input::placeholder, .form-textarea::placeholder { color: var(--dim); }
  .btn-submit { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; background: var(--accent); color: var(--black); border: none; padding: 16px 40px; cursor: crosshair; transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 8px; }
  .btn-submit:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,229,160,0.25); }
  .contact-info { padding-top: 16px; }
  .contact-line { padding: 24px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
  .contact-line:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .contact-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: var(--dim); text-transform: uppercase; }
  .contact-value { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--text); letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  .contact-value a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
  .disclaimer { margin-top: 48px; padding: 24px 32px; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--panel); }
  .disclaimer p { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.62rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--dim); letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  .disclaimer p strong { color: var(--muted); font-weight: 500; }

  footer { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 32px 48px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .footer-copy { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--dim); }
  .footer-logo { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.2rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--dim); text-decoration: none; }
  .footer-logo span { color: var(--accent); }

  @keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); transition: opacity 0.7s, transform 0.7s; }
  .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  .live-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; animation: pulse 1.8s infinite; }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); } 50% { opacity: 0.4; transform: scale(0.7); } }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    nav { padding: 16px 24px; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    #hero, #approach, #philosophy, #rules, #about, #contact { padding-left: 24px; padding-right: 24px; }
    .approach-grid, .philosophy-inner, .rules-layout, .about-grid, .contact-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
    .stats-bar { display: none; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a href="#" class="logo">Fastball<span>.</span>Futures</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#approach">Approach</a></li>
    <li><a href="#philosophy">Philosophy</a></li>
    <li><a href="#rules">Rules</a></li>
    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
  <button class="nav-cta" onclick="document.getElementById('contact').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Get In Touch</button>
</nav>

<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-grid-lines"></div>
  <div class="hero-orb"></div>
  <div class="hero-ticker"><span class="live-dot"></span>Intraday Precision Trading</div>
  <h1 class="hero-headline">Play the<br><span class="accent">Base Hit.</span><br><span class="stroke">Win the Game.</span></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Disciplined intraday trading built on the Moneyball philosophy — consistent small gains, rigorous risk management, and zero room for ego.</p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a href="#approach" class="btn-primary">Our Approach</a>
    <a href="#philosophy" class="btn-ghost">See the Playbook</a>
  </div>
  <div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-value"><span>73</span>%</div><div class="stat-label">Win Rate Target</div></div>
    <div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-value">2<span>:</span>1</div><div class="stat-label">Min Risk / Reward</div></div>
    <div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-value"><span>&lt;</span></div><div class="stat-label">Max Risk Per Trade</div></div>
    <div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-value">Base<span>+</span></div><div class="stat-label">Strategy Framework</div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="approach">
  <div class="section-tag">Method</div>
  <h2 class="section-headline">The <em>Edge</em> Is Discipline</h2>
  <div class="approach-grid">
    <div class="approach-card reveal">
      <div class="card-num">01</div>
      <div class="card-title">Moneyball Mindset</div>
      <p class="card-body">We don't swing for the fences. Like Beane's Oakland A's, we find the inefficiencies others ignore — small, repeatable setups with a statistical edge that compounds quietly over time.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="approach-card reveal">
      <div class="card-num">02</div>
      <div class="card-title">Risk First, Always</div>
      <p class="card-body">Every position is sized before entry. Risk per trade depends on setup, hard stops, no averaging down. Capital preservation is the only job — the profits follow naturally from staying in the game.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="approach-card reveal">
      <div class="card-num">03</div>
      <div class="card-title">Process Over Outcome</div>
      <p class="card-body">A losing trade executed with perfect discipline is a win. An undisciplined winner is a warning sign. We grade ourselves on process, not P&L — the numbers take care of themselves.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="philosophy">
  <div class="philosophy-inner">
    <div class="philosophy-text reveal">
      <div class="section-tag">Philosophy</div>
      <div class="big-quote">Singles and doubles<br><span class="highlight">beat home runs</span><br>every season.</div>
      <p class="philosophy-body">The market rewards patience and punishes ego. Fastball Futures was built on one simple truth: a consistent 1–2% daily gain compounds into something remarkable, while one reckless position can undo months of work.<br><br>We trade intraday. We take what the market gives. We never force it.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="scorecard reveal">
      <div style="height:32px;"></div>
      <div class="trade-row">
        <div><div class="trade-ticker">MNQ</div><div class="trade-type">Long · Call · 0DTE</div></div>
        <div class="trade-result"><div class="trade-pnl win">+$380</div><div class="trade-size">Sized: 1.8% risk</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="trade-row">
        <div><div class="trade-ticker">MES</div><div class="trade-type">Short · Put · 1DTE</div></div>
        <div class="trade-result"><div class="trade-pnl win">+$215</div><div class="trade-size">Sized: 1.2% risk</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="trade-row">
        <div><div class="trade-ticker">MYM</div><div class="trade-type">Long · Call · 2DTE</div></div>
        <div class="trade-result"><div class="trade-pnl loss">-$140</div><div class="trade-size">Sized: 1.5% risk</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="trade-row">
        <div><div class="trade-ticker">MGC</div><div class="trade-type">Long · Put · 0DTE</div></div>
        <div class="trade-result"><div class="trade-pnl win">+$290</div><div class="trade-size">Sized: 1.6% risk</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="scorecard-footer">
        <div><div class="win-rate">75%</div><div class="win-rate-label">Today's Win Rate</div></div>
        <div class="win-bar"><div class="win-bar-label">Win / Loss Ratio</div><div class="win-bar-track"><div class="win-bar-fill"></div></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="rules">
  <div class="rules-layout">
    <div class="rules-sticky">
      <div class="section-tag">The Rulebook</div>
      <h2 class="section-headline">Non-<em>Negotiable</em></h2>
      <p style="font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:300;line-height:1.8;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:0.03em;">Rules aren't restrictions — they're the structure that makes freedom possible. These are ours.</p>
    </div>
    <ul class="rules-list">
      <li class="reveal"><span class="rule-counter"></span><div><div class="rule-title">Never Risk More Than 2% Per Trade</div><p class="rule-desc">Position sizing is calculated before entry, always. A 2% max risk means you can lose 50 trades in a row and still have half your account. That's staying power. That's the game.</p></div></li>
      <li class="reveal"><span class="rule-counter"></span><div><div class="rule-title">Stop Losses Are Not Suggestions</div><p class="rule-desc">A stop is a pre-planned exit, not a prayer. It gets set at entry and it doesn't move — ever. Hoping a loser turns around is how careers end. We let the thesis play out or we exit.</p></div></li>
      <li class="reveal"><span class="rule-counter"></span><div><div class="rule-title">Take the Single, Don't Wait for the Homer</div><p class="rule-desc">A clean 1.5R winner taken quickly beats an emotional 3R winner held too long every time. We take profits when the plan says to take profits — not when it feels exciting.</p></div></li>
      <li class="reveal"><span class="rule-counter"></span><div><div class="rule-title">No Trades In the First 15 Minutes</div><p class="rule-desc">The open is noise. Institutions are filling orders, algos are hunting stops, retail is panicking. We wait for the dust to settle and let the real price action reveal itself.</p></div></li>
      <li class="reveal"><span class="rule-counter"></span><div><div class="rule-title">Log Every Trade, Good and Bad</div><p class="rule-desc">The trade journal is the most valuable tool in the kit. Patterns emerge. Biases reveal themselves. You can't improve what you don't measure — this is Moneyball 101.</p></div></li>
      <li class="reveal"><span class="rule-counter"></span><div><div class="rule-title">Walk Away After 3 Losses</div><p class="rule-desc">Three consecutive stops is a signal — either the market isn't giving what we need today, or the mental state is off. Either way, the right move is the same: close the platform, reset.</p></div></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="about">
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div>
      <div class="section-tag">About</div>
      <h2 class="section-headline">Built On<br><em>Patience</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="about-body">
        <p>Fastball Futures was founded on a deceptively simple premise: <strong>the best traders don't swing harder, they swing smarter.</strong> Inspired by the Moneyball revolution in baseball — where on-base percentage was worth more than batting average — we brought that same data-driven discipline to intraday markets.</p>
        <p>We don't chase. We don't revenge trade. We don't blow up accounts trying to recover yesterday's losses. We show up every day with a plan, execute with precision, and go home flat.</p>
